<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="flow-vi">flow <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fləʊ/    美 /floʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(液体、气体、电等) 流动；流出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It's here that the river <strong>flows down</strong> into the ocean.
这条河就在这里流入海洋。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>流逝；畅通；流淌：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Time flows away. 
光阴流逝。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her hair flowed down over her shoulders.
她的头发垂到肩上。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Trucks and cars flowed along the highway.
卡车和汽车在公路上川流不息。</p></div></div>